</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_154" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_154_r2l12"><expan>Hartpreht<ex>en</ex></expan> Harſkircher </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><note place="marginleft"><ab facs="#facs_154_r1l1">Non ſunt <expan>p<ex>raeſe</ex>ntate</expan></ab></note>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l14">Lıeber her Harſkircher / vns 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> iſt <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l15">woꝛden / vvie daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Hercʒog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Amptleut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l16">
<del rend="strikethrough">dem Berhtold Deihſler </del> etlichen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgern</ex></expan> vnd <expan>kauffleute<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l17">Jr hab vnd kauffmanſchaft <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd gen vvald </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l18">
<del rend="strikethrough">getrib </del> gefürt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Darynne Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"> euch </del> Jn gar fürderlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l20">geweſen / vnd euch darümb 
<add><ab facs="#facs_154_line_1575554178976_48"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> vaſt gemüet habt / des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l21">wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ dancken / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l22">daʒ Jr fürbaʒ aber 
<del rend="strikethrough">den </del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hılff vnd furdrung 
<del rend="strikethrough"> gen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l23">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Hercʒog <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </del> darcʒu tun wöllet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l24"><expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ~ dieſelb Jr habe vnd kauffman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r2l26">ſchaft 
<add><ab facs="#facs_154_line_1575554288912_64">
<del rend="strikethrough">vvıder vverde </del></ab></add> on hındernüſſe volge Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_154" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hartpreht<ex>en</ex></expan> Harskircher </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="marginleft">Non sunt
                                <expan>p<ex>raese</ex>ntate</expan>.</note>
</app>Lieber her Harskircher, uns ist <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        gesagt worden, wie daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                        amptleut etlichen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> und <expan>kauffleute<ex>n</ex></expan> ir
                        hab und kauffmanschaft <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und gen Wald
                        gefürt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darynne ir in gar fürderlich gewesen
                        und euch darümb <add><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add> vast gemüet habt, des wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                        dancken. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir fürbaz aber
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hilff und furdrung darczu tun wöllet
                                <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        dieselb ir habe und kauffmanschaft on hindernüsse volge, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab></div>
</div></body>
